@startuml
[*] --> WaitingCustomer

state "Waiting for customer" as WaitingCustomer
state "Recording items" as RecordItems
state "Waiting for payment" as WaitingPayment
state "Sale completed" as SaleComplete

WaitingCustomer --> RecordItems : enter item
RecordItems --> RecordItems : enter item
RecordItems --> WaitingPayment : end of sale
WaitingPayment --> SaleComplete : cash payment
WaitingPayment --> VerifyingPayment : card/check payment
VerifyingPayment --> SaleComplete : payment approved
SaleComplete --> WaitingCustomer : next customer

note right of RecordItems
The system records items one by one
as they are selected by the customer
end note

note right of VerifyingPayment
The system verifies payment details
for card or check transactions
end note
@enduml
